body:
Hey Guys, so I just restarted my youtube channel and am wanting some suggestions on what I should do for a first video. So if you have any suggestions, let me know and I will give you a shout out if I choose the kind of video you suggested! Please nothing inappropriate and don't copy other peoples ideas! Thx guys, You're the Best!!!

- Sheamus
